{
  "chapter": 82,
  "chapter_summary": "本章\"无心铸大错\"围绕李寻欢与上官金虹的决战展开。孙小红与李寻欢对话中透露孙老先生对上官金虹的愤怒却迟迟不出手的隐忧，李寻欢推断孙老先生可能因武功巅峰而产生恐惧、失去锐气。二人狂奔赶往长亭，却发现坐在亭中抽旱烟的并非孙老先生，而是上官金虹——他已杀了孙老先生。荆无命携林仙儿出现，林仙儿怂恿荆无命趁上官金虹与李寻欢对决时出手，荆无命却反将林仙儿擒住，揭露其右手并未残废的秘密。上官金虹承认自己看错、做错，但仍保持冷酷对峙。林仙儿试图挑拨三人关系，揭露荆无命对上官金虹的病态忠诚，最终被荆无命摔在上官金虹脚下。四人在暗夜长亭中形成微妙的对峙格局，胜负悬于荆无命之手。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "但那只不过是因为他根本没有机会使用武功，也没有必要使用武功。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 82,
      "line_start": 2,
      "line_end": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "没有必要？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 82,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "因为他根本没有对手。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 82,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "上官金虹呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 82,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "他也……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 82,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "上官金虹的所做所为，你爷爷是否已觉得不能忍受？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 82,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "他……他的确对上官金虹很愤怒。",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 82,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "但他却没有向上官金虹下手。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 82,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "他没有……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 82,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "他为什么一直在忍受？为什么要等你去求他时才肯出手？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 82,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "你……你难道认为他老人家……",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 82,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "一个人的武功若是到了巅峰，心里就会产生一种恐惧，生怕别人会赶上他，生怕自己会退步，到了这种时候，他往往会想法子逃避，什么事都不敢去做。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 82,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "越不去做，就渐渐会变得真的不能做了，有些人就会忽然归隐，有些人甚至会变得自暴自弃，甚至一死了之……自古以来，这样的例子已有很多，除非他真的能超然物外，做到‘太上忘情’的地步，对世上所有的一切事都不再关心。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 82,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "但愿我的想法不对，只不过……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 82,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "求求你，带我赶回去，只要能及时赶到那里，无论要我做什么我都愿意。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 82,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "爷爷，我们回来了……我们回来了！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 82,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "很好，我正在等着你们！",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 82,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "你来晚了。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 82,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "我来晚了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 82,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "来晚了总比不来的好。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 82,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "你本该知道我迟早总要来的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 82,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "只可惜该来的人来迟，不该来的人反而先来了。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 82,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "text": "你若要杀他，现在就是最好的机会，再好也没有了。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 82,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "荆无命",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "现在已有人杀他，用不着我出手。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 82,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "text": "我不是要你去杀李寻欢。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 82,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "荆无命",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "杀谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 82,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "text": "上官金虹，杀上官金虹！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 82,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "text": "他现在正全心全意要对付李寻欢，绝没有余力再对付别人，何况，他还不知道你右手的秘密，你一定可以杀了他！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 82,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "text": "金钱帮的秘密，只有你知道得最多，你杀了他，你就是金钱帮的帮主。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 82,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "text": "你就算不想当金钱帮的帮主，但也该让他看看你的厉害，让他下了地狱后还要后悔，以前为什么那样对待你。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 82,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "text": "去，快去，错过这机会，后悔的就是你，而不是他了。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 82,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "荆无命",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "好，我去！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 82,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "text": "快去吧，我就在这里等着你，只要你成功，我以后就永远是你的人了。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 82,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "荆无命",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "你用不着等我。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 82,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 82,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "荆无命",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "因为你也要跟我一起去！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 82,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "text": "我做错了什么？你要这样对我？",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 82,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "荆无命",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "你这一生中，也许只做错了一件事。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 82,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "text": "什么事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 82,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "荆无命",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "你不该认为每个人都和阿飞一样爱你！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 82,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "荆无命",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "也许我可以帮你杀了李寻欢，也可以帮他杀了你。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 82,
      "line_start": 364,
      "line_end": 366
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "text": "我相信你可以。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 82,
      "line_start": 368,
      "line_end": 368
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "荆无命",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "你相信？在你眼中，我岂非已是个残废？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 82,
      "line_start": 370,
      "line_end": 370
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "text": "每个人都有看错的时候。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 82,
      "line_start": 372,
      "line_end": 372
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "荆无命",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "你怎么知道你看错了？也许我的确是个残废。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 82,
      "line_start": 374,
      "line_end": 374
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "text": "你的右手比左手更有力。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 82,
      "line_start": 376,
      "line_end": 376
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "荆无命",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "你看得出？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 82,
      "line_start": 378,
      "line_end": 378
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "text": "林仙儿并不是个弱不禁风的女人，无论谁想要用一只手制住她，都不容易。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 82,
      "line_start": 380,
      "line_end": 382
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "荆无命",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "你果然看出来了，只可惜太迟了些。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 82,
      "line_start": 384,
      "line_end": 386
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "text": "我不但看错，也做错了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 82,
      "line_start": 388,
      "line_end": 388
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "荆无命",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "你也知道不该那样对我？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 82,
      "line_start": 390,
      "line_end": 390
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "text": "我的确不该那样对你，我本该杀了你的！",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 82,
      "line_start": 392,
      "line_end": 392
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "荆无命",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "你为什么没有杀？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 82,
      "line_start": 394,
      "line_end": 394
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "text": "我不忍。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 82,
      "line_start": 396,
      "line_end": 396
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "荆无命",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "你也有不忍的时候？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 82,
      "line_start": 398,
      "line_end": 400
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "text": "我也是人。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 82,
      "line_start": 402,
      "line_end": 402
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "荆无命",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "所以你认为我也不忍杀你？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 82,
      "line_start": 404,
      "line_end": 404
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "text": "她一定也想要你来杀我。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 82,
      "line_start": 406,
      "line_end": 406
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "荆无命",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "不错。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 82,
      "line_start": 408,
      "line_end": 408
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "text": "你若真要杀我，就不会将她带来了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 82,
      "line_start": 410,
      "line_end": 410
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "他的确不敢杀你，因为你若死了，他也活不下去，我现在才明白，他这人本就是为你而活着的，他到这里来，就为了要在你面前证明他自己是多么重要，可是在别人眼里，他根本连一文都不值。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 82,
      "line_start": 416,
      "line_end": 418
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "但他要杀你却很容易。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 82,
      "line_start": 420,
      "line_end": 420
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "你以为他敢杀我？……你要杀我，他却救了我，你可知道是为了什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 82,
      "line_start": 422,
      "line_end": 424
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "因为他要亲手在我面前杀你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 82,
      "line_start": 426,
      "line_end": 426
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "你错了，他并不是要自己亲手杀我，而是要看你亲手杀我……",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 82,
      "line_start": 428,
      "line_end": 428
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "我和你在一起的时候，他嫉妒得发疯，那时我本以为他是为了我，现在我才知道他是为了你，只要是你喜欢的人，他都恨，甚至连你的儿子也不例外……你可知道你儿子是谁杀死的？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 82,
      "line_start": 430,
      "line_end": 432
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "他若是为了我而杀人，无论杀谁都没关系。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 82,
      "line_start": 434,
      "line_end": 436
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我一向总认为我很能了解男人，可是我却实在不了解你们，实在想不通你们两个人究竟是什么样的关系。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 82,
      "line_start": 438,
      "line_end": 440
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我只知道无论那是种什么样活见鬼的关系，都一定令人恶心得要命，所以你们就算想告诉我，我也不想听。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 82,
      "line_start": 442,
      "line_end": 444
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "你知道的不多，说的却太多了。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 82,
      "line_start": 446,
      "line_end": 446
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "但我无论说什么，也没法子要你杀他的，是不是？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 82,
      "line_start": 448,
      "line_end": 448
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "你没法子！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 82,
      "line_start": 450,
      "line_end": 450
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "text": "我当然也没法子要你杀他，是不是？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 82,
      "line_start": 452,
      "line_end": 454
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "荆无命",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 82,
      "line_start": 456,
      "line_end": 456
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "看来我只有让你们两个人来杀我了，问题是谁动手呢？是他，还是你？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 82,
      "line_start": 458,
      "line_end": 460
    }
  ],
